import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Link } from 'docz';

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"use-react"}}>{`use-react`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"primitives"}}>{`Primitives`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">
<Link to="/use-array">useArray</Link>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">
<Link to="/use-object">useObject</Link>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag></MDXTag>
